{"id":12303,"date":"2020-09-04T14:12:28","date_gmt":"2020-09-04T14:12:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/?page_id=12303"},"modified":"2020-09-28T09:25:09","modified_gmt":"2020-09-28T09:25:09","slug":"limportance-de-la-normalisation","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/normalisation\/limportance-de-la-normalisation\/","title":{"rendered":"L&rsquo;importance de la Normalisation"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"limit-wrapper\"><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  wpv-first-level first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-598ec59800f6046bec0cebe61cff90cd\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-ce278d3731670055627d8f96be917f47\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended has-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-a43d3325d27cf391dc3c904a9be4a09c\" ><div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-1  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-41c6bdf5bce9dedd5e090f5a53ae4e4c\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"first\"><img width=\"1000\" height=\"250\" src=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/importance_normalisation.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full\" alt=\"\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/importance_normalisation.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/importance_normalisation-600x150.jpg 600w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/importance_normalisation-300x75.jpg 300w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/importance_normalisation-768x192.jpg 768w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/importance_normalisation-800x200.jpg 800w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/importance_normalisation-555x139.jpg 555w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/importance_normalisation-360x90.jpg 360w, https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/09\/importance_normalisation-262x66.jpg 262w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\" \/><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>L&rsquo;IMPORTANCE DE LA NORMALISATION<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p>La mondialisation des \u00e9changes, l\u2019interp\u00e9n\u00e9tration des technologies et la globalisation des questions d\u2019environnement et de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 rendent plus que jamais utile le d\u00e9veloppement de normes. La normalisation appara\u00eet en effet comme un outil particuli\u00e8rement adapt\u00e9 pour accompagner ces \u00e9volutions. Ces \u00e9volutions vont toutes dans le sens d\u2019un plus grand recours \u00e0 la normalisation volontaire, c\u2019est-\u00e0-dire \u00e0 l\u2019\u00e9tablissement de r\u00e8gles \u00e9labor\u00e9es en commun par les acteurs eux-m\u00eames, leur permettant d\u2019\u00e9changer et d\u2019assurer que la concurrence peut s\u2019exercer sur des bases connues et accept\u00e9es, garantes d\u2019un march\u00e9 ouvert. En effet la normalisation garantie\u00a0:<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-9ccc7c8c906f431ddc50c1d12cc966fb\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">D\u00e9veloppement les march\u00e9s<\/h3>\n<p>Elle joue un r\u00f4le essentiel dans les \u00e9changes commerciaux, en facilitant la libre circulation des produits. La norme permet le d\u00e9veloppement des march\u00e9s en harmonisant les r\u00e8gles et les pratiques et en r\u00e9duisant les entraves techniques aux \u00e9changes.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-b67430ca0b874971232a855997c0c67e\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Clarification des transactions<\/h3>\n<p>La norme aide \u00e0 la d\u00e9finition des besoins, optimise les relations clients\/fournisseurs, fournit un r\u00e9f\u00e9rentiel pour la valorisation des produits et services et permet l\u2019\u00e9conomie d\u2019essais compl\u00e9mentaires.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-fbf827d786ff113cb8e942dbadcf7bcb\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Rationalisation de la production<\/h3>\n<p>Les entreprises peuvent mettre \u00e0 profit le r\u00e9sultat d\u2019ann\u00e9es d\u2019exp\u00e9rience pour obtenir des produits conformes, compatibles et interchangeables et mieux g\u00e9rer leurs approvisionnements et leurs stocks.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-aaaa24653c45134338030d3ba1a633df\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">S\u00e9curisation de l\u2019entreprise<\/h3>\n<p>La norme contribue \u00e0 s\u00e9curiser l\u2019entreprise vis-\u00e0-vis de sa responsabilit\u00e9 g\u00e9n\u00e9rale sur les produits mis sur le march\u00e9.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-d7ffd27fb2b9339dd2dec0446a5a5bbc\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Choix strat\u00e9giques<\/h3>\n<p>La norme est un outil simplificateur qui permet aux entreprises de resserrer le nombre de types de produits existants et d\u2019augmenter les volumes de production sur des s\u00e9ries plus longues.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-ffd00685f43a3859e47e06275f06fa2d\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Protection des consommateurs<\/h3>\n<p>La norme est un facteur important de l\u2019am\u00e9lioration de la qualit\u00e9 des produits et services offerts aux consommateurs. Elle permet d\u2019appliquer des m\u00e9thodes reconnues, pour obtenir un niveau optimal de qualit\u00e9, de fiabilit\u00e9 et de s\u00e9curit\u00e9.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"row \"><div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  first unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-cc0f1dc282da01f7c8450edf65e4249c\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Application de la r\u00e9glementation<\/h3>\n<p>Certains domaines font l\u2019objet de r\u00e9glementations qui s\u2019appuient sur des normes. La norme fournit les moyens techniques pour satisfaire aux exigences de la s\u00e9curit\u00e9 r\u00e9glementaire.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-c22a35152f13a7e470fabd77cada7586\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div>\n<div class=\"wpv-grid grid-1-3  unextended no-extended-padding\" style=\"padding-top:0.05px;padding-bottom:0.05px;\" id=\"wpv-column-211aa71084c182fd8ecee9bd879a667b\" >\n<div  data-target=\"_self\" class=\"linkarea clearfix accent5  background-transparent\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"last\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><div class=\"push \" style=\"height:10px\"><\/div><\/div>\n\t<\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":11851,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_mi_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/12303"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/aganorgabon.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"abou